013578*2212-COUNT-APPL-COMP.
013578*---------------------
013578*
013578*    IF RAPPL-CO-ID = MIR-CO-ID
013578*        ADD +1             TO WS-APPL-COMP-COUNT
013578*    END-IF.
013578*
013578*    PERFORM  APPL-2000-READ-NEXT
013578*        THRU APPL-2000-READ-NEXT-X.
013578*
013578*2212-COUNT-APPL-COMP-X.
