               MOVE 'XS00000006'      TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
               SET MIR-RETRN-RQST-FAILED TO TRUE
