       2330-UPDATE-EDITS.
      *-----------------

           MOVE ZERO                  TO WGLOB-MSG-ERROR-SW.

           IF MIR-APPL-EDIT-LANG-CD NOT = SPACE
               PERFORM  2335-EDIT-ELANG
                   THRU 2335-EDIT-ELANG-X
           ELSE
               MOVE RAPPL-APPL-EDIT-LANG-CD
