013578*            THRU 2340-EDIT-EXIT-PGM-X
013578*    ELSE
013578*        MOVE RAPPL-APPL-EXIT-PGM-ID
013578*                               TO MIR-APPL-EXIT-PGM-ID
013578*    END-IF.

554712*    IF MIR-DV-APPL-ID-TXT > SPACES
554712*        IF MIR-DV-APPL-ID-TXT = EBLCH-BLANK-FIELD-CHAR
554712*            MOVE SPACES              TO RAPPL-APPL-DESC-TXT
554712*            MOVE SPACES              TO MIR-DV-APPL-ID-TXT
554712*        ELSE
554712*            MOVE MIR-DV-APPL-ID-TXT        TO RAPPL-APPL-DESC-TXT
554712*        END-IF
554712*    ELSE
554712*        MOVE RAPPL-APPL-DESC-TXT     TO MIR-DV-APPL-ID-TXT
554712*    END-IF.

           PERFORM  2345-EDIT-CTRY-AND-CURR
               THRU 2345-EDIT-CTRY-AND-CURR-X
               VARYING SUB1 FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL   SUB1 > +5.

           PERFORM  2355-CHK-DUPLICATE-CTRY-CURR
               THRU 2355-CHK-DUPLICATE-CTRY-CURR-X
               VARYING CTRY-IDX1 FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL   CTRY-IDX1 > +5.

           IF WGLOB-MSG-ERROR-SW = ZERO
               MOVE ZERO              TO CTRY-IDX2
               PERFORM  2390-PACK-CTRY-AND-CURR
                   THRU 2390-PACK-CTRY-AND-CURR-X
                   VARYING CTRY-IDX1 FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   CTRY-IDX1 > +5

54-001     END-IF.

           MOVE LOW-VALUES            TO MIR-APPL-ASCL-REL-CTR.

       2330-UPDATE-EDITS-X.
           EXIT.

