      *--------------------
       2400-PROCESS-DELETE.
      *--------------------

013578*    MOVE MIR-APPL-ID           TO WAPPL-APPL-ID.
013578     MOVE WGLOB-COMPANY-CODE    TO WS-CO-ID.
013578     MOVE MIR-CO-ID             TO WGLOB-COMPANY-CODE.
           MOVE MIR-CO-ID             TO WAPPL-CO-ID.
           PERFORM  APPL-1000-READ-FOR-UPDATE
               THRU APPL-1000-READ-FOR-UPDATE-X.
013578     MOVE WS-CO-ID              TO WGLOB-COMPANY-CODE.

           IF WAPPL-IO-OK
               CONTINUE
           ELSE
               MOVE WAPPL-KEY         TO WGLOB-MSG-PARM (1)
               MOVE 'XS00000010'      TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
               SET MIR-RETRN-RQST-FAILED TO TRUE
               GO TO 2400-PROCESS-DELETE-X
54-001     END-IF.

           IF RAPPL-APPL-ASCL-REL-CTR  > ZERO
               PERFORM  APPL-3000-UNLOCK
                   THRU APPL-3000-UNLOCK-X
               PERFORM  9200-MOVE-RECORD-TO-SCREEN
                   THRU 9200-MOVE-RECORD-TO-SCREEN-X
               SET MIR-RETRN-RQST-FAILED TO TRUE
               MOVE 'XS01500011'      TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
               GO TO 2400-PROCESS-DELETE-X
54-001     END-IF.

           PERFORM  APPL-1000-DELETE
               THRU APPL-1000-DELETE-X.
           MOVE 'XS00000011'          TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO.
           PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
               THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X.

           PERFORM  9100-BLANK-DATA-FIELDS
               THRU 9100-BLANK-DATA-FIELDS-X.

       2400-PROCESS-DELETE-X.
           EXIT.

013578*--------------------
013578*2500-PROCESS-LIST.
013578*--------------------
013578*
013578*    MOVE SPACES                    TO MIR-APPL-ID-G.
013578*    MOVE SPACES                    TO MIR-CO-ID-G.
013578*    MOVE SPACES                TO MIR-APPL-ID-G.
013578*    MOVE SPACES                TO MIR-CO-ID-G.
013578*    MOVE SPACES                TO MIR-APPL-CTRY-10-CD-G.
013578*    MOVE SPACES                TO MIR-APPL-CRCY-10-5-CD-G.
013578*
